This product includes software developed at minish.ai (Agent-tools).

The `agent_cli/code_index/` package is a derivative work of `tsindex.py`
from minish.ai/Agent-tools (Apache License 2.0). Modifications include:

  - Splitting the single-file CLI into a package
    (schema/builder/store/callgraph/slice/preproc + per-language walkers).
  - Adding a `section` kind and a tree-sitter-markdown walker.
  - Integrating with agent-cli's tool registry as a native tool
    (`code_index`) with mode dispatch.
  - Wiring lazy build + per-query incremental rebuild
    (sha1 compare) + edit/write post-hook invalidation
    into the agent loop.
  - Hashline-format output wrapper for `mode='fetch'` and `mode='slice'`
    so `edit_file` accepts the output directly.
  - On-demand parse fallback for paths outside the indexed root.

Each source file in `agent_cli/code_index/` carries an `Originally
ported from minish.ai/Agent-tools tsindex.py (Apache 2.0).` header.
